// Sutra corpus test: slot declarations.
//
// `slot TYPE name = expr;` — rotation-bound storage in the
// synthetic subspace. The surface syntax parses cleanly today;
// codegen integration that threads slot state through function
// scopes is deferred (the codegen rejects with SUT0150).

function void DeclareSlots() {
    slot int counter = 0;
    slot scalar threshold = 0.5;
    slot vector state;
}
